A basic calculator web app built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

✨ Features
Perform addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division

Clear (AC) and delete (DEL) functions

Support for decimal numbers and double zero (00)

Responsive and modern user interface

📁 Files
index.html – Contains the main HTML structure

style.css – Defines the calculator’s styles

script.js – (Optional) External JS file for logic (currently unused; logic is inline in HTML)

▶️ Usage
Download or clone the repository

Open index.html in your web browser

Start calculating!

🛠️ Customization
Move inline JavaScript to script.js for better structure

Modify styles in style.css to customize the look

📄 License
This project is open-source and free to use.

